{"tid":1292450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無變形] 三峽大瀑布景區宣布暫停營業 稱因上游施工截流","createTime":"2019-07-07T10:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T11:42:20.000Z","uid":79562,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1d112363c55fa865e9535ea47b6cb6828780b7eb","tid":1292450,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"撰文：姜庚宇<br />\n2019-07-07 17:46<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-07-07 17:46<br />\n三峽大壩「發生變形並可能潰壩」的消息本月1日開始瘋傳，三峽集團就回應指消息失實，強調大壩並未變形。<br />\n<br />\n不過，三峽大瀑布景區就剛好發通知指，「目前景區已經停止營業了，因為上游建設施工進入的截流階段，所以瀑布斷流了，沒辦法接待遊客。」與傳言時間上的吻合引發聯想。<br />\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/2019/0707/20190707125956103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimg2.huanqiu.com%2Fattachment2010%2F2019%2F0707%2F20190707125956103.jpg&h=94d6c566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通知指，三峽大瀑布景區上游建設施工，導致瀑布斷流。（北京頭條）<br />\n<br />\n一份湖北宜昌三峽大瀑布景區上周五（5日）發布的通知顯示，因上游建設施工進入截流階段，導致瀑布斷流，景區從7月6日起停業至7月13日，期間將暫停接待遊客，恢復營業時間另行通知。在暫停營業期間，景區將暫停接待年卡遊客。<br />\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/2019/0707/20190707125956205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimg2.huanqiu.com%2Fattachment2010%2F2019%2F0707%2F20190707125956205.jpg&h=b98e77e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料顯示，三峽大瀑布原名白果樹瀑布，被譽為「中國十大名瀑」的第4大瀑布，是國家4A級旅遊景區。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，三峽大壩日前傳出已經變形，但三峽集團負責人很快回應強調，網傳Google地圖上的衛星圖片，是通過拍攝的多張圖片，結合地理座標等資訊，經過拼接修正後生成，與事實不符。<br />\n<br />\n三峽集團周日（7日）正式回應大壩變形傳聞，表示大壩運行以來的監測資料表明，各建築物工作性態正常，截至2019年4月，壩基累計垂直位移在1.45-26.69毫米之間，工程運行安全可靠。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/349138/%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E5%A4%A7%E7%80%91%E5%B8%83%E6%99%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD-%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%8A%E6%B8%B8%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%AA%E6%B5%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F349138%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2580%2591%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%2599%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2587%259F%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%259B%25A0%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%25B5%2581&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a79197cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/349138/%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E5%A4%A7%E7%80%91%E5%B8%83%E6%99%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD-%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%8A%E6%B8%B8%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%AA%E6%B5%81</a>"},{"pid":"5c99b13232aa95516f9a8cdb62216e31ad9b6e48","tid":1292450,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d642679adc40b378eebb621e74024aa5430f3e","tid":1292450,"uid":108133,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"等睇世紀大瀑布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9943ab3812b8ad009aff2391e03b728e192895a4","tid":1292450,"uid":119653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔通真係彎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1694f049aaca345f5f2e417120eebd8cb4dfe73","tid":1292450,"uid":33933,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"其實真係無乜可能變形到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家小心炒車"},{"pid":"ea3578af0507fffa3c960c3764de8f4e8caf3fad","tid":1292450,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"GPS 同 GoogleMap 變形<br />\n大壩可擋億年一遇天災"},{"pid":"fe28291020e1a29fed7199e6ebf3377b93f2c4c5","tid":1292450,"uid":58552,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"r